# Frontend UI Specification

## Design System

The frontend uses a centralized CSS design system defined in `backend/frontend/src/index.css`. All UI elements must derive their visual foundation from shared tokens and utility classes. This ensures visual consistency and allows smaller models to compose UI reliably from a small set of primitives.

